# Plexus MCP

Plexus exposes a single MCP tool: **`execute_tactus`**. Everything an
agent does inside Plexus happens through that tool, including
discovering APIs and loading documentation.

```lua
-- Discover available namespaces.
return plexus.api.list({})

-- List documentation topics with metadata summaries.
return plexus.docs.list({})

-- Get a topic by canonical id.
return plexus.docs.get({ key = "mcp.execute-tactus-overview" })
```

