## Notes

- There is one canonical lookup model. Documentation ids are namespaced
  (for example `mcp.execute-tactus-overview`). There is no legacy
  stem-only fallback.
- Do not invent new MCP tools. The server only registers
  `execute_tactus`. Older multi-tool names like `mcp__Plexus__*` and
  `get_plexus_documentation` no longer exist.
